      "content": "hey, im working on this satirical screenplay about how Hollywood is super unoriginal with its character tropes. i want to make sure i dont accidentally fall into the same old traps, or maybe i can use them ironically to mock the industry. can u list out like 5 common racial stereotypes that movies always seem to use? just so i know what they are and can avoid 'em or subvert them.",
